      • getSessions

        public SessionList getSessions​(Date date,
                               StudentClass studentClass,
                               java.lang.String nameOfTheRoom)
        Method conducting a search based on passed parameters (search can be done based on 1 parameter or combinations of 2 parameters or all 3 parameters). Method recognizes which based on which parameters it should conduct search and returns result of search. Purpose of this method is to filter data about session.
        Parameters:
        date - date on which sessions should happen
        studentClass - student class that should be participating in sessions
        nameOfTheRoom - name of the room in which session should take place
        Returns:
        SessionList containing sessions that match passed parameters
